sherpa-onnx
  Project:  https://github.com/k2-fsa/sherpa-onnx
  Author:   The k2-fsa / Next-gen Kaldi team
  License:  Apache License 2.0
  Use:      On-device VAD, streaming ASR, endpointing, TTS, and speaker
            embeddings (the AudioEngine in core/engines/sherpa.py). The example
            ASR / VAD / TTS / punctuation / speaker-embedding model archives
            fetched by tools/setup_models.py are published from the sherpa-onnx
            GitHub releases and carry their own upstream model licenses.

Silero VAD
  Project:  https://github.com/snakers4/silero-vad
  Author:   Silero Team
  License:  MIT License
  Use:      Voice-activity-detection model (the "vad_model" / silero_vad.onnx
